  <verse number="8" style="v" />In this way we had affection for you. We were pleased to share with you not only the gospel of God but also our own lives. For you had become very dear to us.

  <verse number="9" style="v" />For you remember, brothers, our labor and toil. Night and day we were working so that we might not weigh down any of you. During that time, we preached to you the gospel of God.
